an class=\"nowrap-item\">qu\u1ed1c gia<\/span>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                        <div class=\"hv-content\">\r\n                            <ul>\r\n                                <li>\r\n                                    <div class=\"hv-box\">\r\n                                        <div class=\"hv-image\"><img src=\"\/sites\/bumas\/images\/pages\/home\/img-value-1.svg\" class=\"img-responsive\" atl=\"Gi\u00fap \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n, c\u01a1 quan t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh\" \/><\/div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"hv-name\"> Gi\u00fap \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n, c\u01a1 quan <span class=\"nowrap-item\">t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh<\/span><\/div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"hv-list\">\r\n                                            <div class=\"hv-item\"> Ban h\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5, danh m\u1ee5c thu, chi th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t <span class=\"nowrap-item\">\u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n<\/span><\/div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"hv-item\"> Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c n\u1eafm <span class=\"hv-highlight\">t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u1ed9p b\u1ea3ng d\u1ef1 to\u00e1n NSNN<\/span> c\u1ee7a c\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 <span class=\"nowrap-item\">nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf<\/span><\/div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"hv-item\"> Nh\u1eadn, ph\u00ea duy\u1ec7t, ph\u00e2n b\u1ed5 d\u1ef1 to\u00e1n, th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cho c\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, <span class=\"nowrap-item\">nhanh ch\u00f3ng<\/span><\/div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"hv-item\"> T\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p 100% d\u1ef1 to\u00e1n NSNN to\u00e0n ng\u00e0nh, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ec9 trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ph\u00fat ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian, <span class=\"nowrap-item\">c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c<\/span><\/div>\r\n                                     